unittitle_ssm: Time Inc. The March of Time Audiovisual Collection
abstract_ssm: The Time Inc. The March of Time Audiovisual Collection contains internal and commercially distributed audiovisual materials that were produced by The March of Time, a division of Time Inc. The materials were created between 1979 and 1995. The majority of records from The March of Time are in the Time Inc. Subject Files (MS 3009-RG 1) and Time Inc. Annex Files (MS 3009-RG 39).
